<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:297px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Dresden_city_center_sights.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/75/Dresden_city_center_sights.png/295px-Dresden_city_center_sights.png" width="295" height="221" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/75/Dresden_city_center_sights.png/443px-Dresden_city_center_sights.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/75/Dresden_city_center_sights.png/590px-Dresden_city_center_sights.png 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Dresden_city_center_sights.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Historic city center with main sights</div>
</div>
